{"tid":1616090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚] 鐘意或者欣賞Catgirl既 入哂嚟！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T00:11:26.000Z","uid":294432,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"58ab540008be99a66b007239e424c24619eab0e0","tid":1616090,"uid":294432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:41:35.000Z","msg":"(我係一位好愛Catgirl既小粉絲，今次好嬲好想為Catgirl出返啖氣！)<br />\nCatgirl今日出左條新片。關於佢俾一位叫 <span style=\"color: red;\">Carmen Ho</span> 既廢老YouTuber，多次係直播侮辱Catgirl，為自己澄清既片段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/isYq0SVmWX4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FisYq0SVmWX4&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=c20871db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/isYq0SVmWX4</a><br />\n<br />\nCarmen Ho同佢個廢老老公以多個謊言或不事實，毫無根據既論點，言語侮辱Catgirl。<br />\n<br />\n當中包括，<br />\n1. 指控Catgirl於大半年前曾Inbox用粗口鬧Carmen Ho，Catgirl澄清從來冇鬧過，並要求對方提出證據。<br />\n<br />\n2. Carmen Ho指控Catgirl曾&rsquo;主動&rsquo;向餐廳要求贊助和免費肥牛，但事實上係餐廳主動送肥牛而且Catgirl有多番拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n3. 話Catgirl既濕疹係生癬和有傳染病。<br />\n<br />\n4. 話Catgirl有精神病。<br />\n等等...<br />\n<br />\nCarmen Ho多次公開侮辱以及人生攻擊公眾人物，毫不證據既情況下為Catgirl添加罪名，傷害他人自尊心，影響聲譽。貶低他人提高自己價值，呢類廢老真係好撚低質。<br />\n<br />\nCatgirl既頻道不論係拍攝技巧還是內容都好撚高質，而且佢既勇氣同毅力並唔係一般人都有，係一位值得欣賞同尊重既公眾人物！Catgirl多次為香港人打氣，出席多個集會活動，希望大家今次都可以為佢爭返啖氣！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DmffrJ7duaI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDmffrJ7duaI&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEnyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=e694ff6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DmffrJ7duaI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條係個仆街廢老既Channel，希望各位巴絲打可以幫手report。我要廢左佢個channel呀屌！"},{"pid":"9ae1982643be6c3d4408646530308af73e9fd04d","tid":1616090,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"aa773c533642f0ffc699686310e1497da932e735","tid":1616090,"uid":44954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1